ModelRelationships
==================

This Rails plugin is a way to define your model relationships in one place.


Example
=======

in environment.rb

ModelRelationships.define([ :Auction, { :children => [:Item,:Donor] } ],
                          [ :Donor, { :children => [:Item] } ],
                          [ :User, { :children => [:Auction] } ],
                          [ :Item ],
                          [ :Note ]
                         )

